⸻

Forbidden Synonyms

To maintain consistency, the following terms are prohibited:

Apartment → Use Unit

Customer → Use Tenant

Client → Use Organization

House → Use Property (unless describing a specific residential property type)

Repair Ticket → Use Maintenance Request

Task → Use Work Order (when maintenance-related)

Employee Account → Use User

Company → Use Organization

